{"tid":2108143,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳云：其實民主派不必辦初選，候選人交給國師，符合民主","createTime":"2020-07-14T10:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T13:22:11.000Z","uid":5843,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"002489a21126ec04dc931d104b02bbe38ab9ba6f","tid":2108143,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"陳雲：我可以給予民主派初選的死亡之吻。經過國師讚貌美如花、衣着配色大方高貴之後（見上星期貼文），黃絲放棄了黨主席黃碧雲。<br />\n黃絲因為憎恨國師，一定放棄國師讚美的民主派候選人。<br />\n其實民主派不必辦初選的，全部候選人交給國師品評，我讚賞的就退選！這種初選不犯法，也符合民主（國師逆向推薦原理！），節省街站資源。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/StszJvO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FStszJvO.png&h=bcc1e096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早兩日，60萬人初選唔符合民主，我推薦邊個入圍就最民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aab982a9d65a78a8237e39ced5a2cdd7a07a042","tid":2108143,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:31:06.000Z","msg":"佢唔玩膠係FB講on9野邊會有人係到轉推佢D post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f965376fb139acb2c48cb8ce05fe56182998b2c0","tid":2108143,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:31:08.000Z","msg":"九東: 陳雲<br />\n九西: 陳雲<br />\n新東: 陳雲<br />\n新西: 陳雲<br />\n超區; 陳雲<br />\n港鳥: 陳雲<br />\n功能組別: 陳雲<br />\n月袋56萬不是萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳雲又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe07af345194cba402bb886d27318608e678ea4b","tid":2108143,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3aab982a9d65a78a8237e39ced5a2cdd7a07a042","tid":2108143,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:31:06.000Z","msg":"佢唔玩膠係FB講on9野邊會有人係到轉推佢D post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"樓豬陳雲信徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/no